      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，秒级精度。那日期格式我用SS，轴标签显示为%S对吗？另外三个section分别对应ID=0、ID=1、ID=2？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dateFormat",
        "section ID=0",
        "section ID=1",
        "section ID=2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，三个section就按这个命名。ID=0下面有三个任务：第一个是8秒，从0开始；然后3秒的任务接在后面；最后2秒的任务再接在3秒之后。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "8s",
        "3s",
        "2s",
        "after 8s",
        "after 3s"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，ID=0部分画好了。那ID=1呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section ID=0"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ID=1也是三个任务：7秒从0开始，然后4秒接在后面，最后1秒的任务——等等，这个1秒任务要在5秒之后开始，不是紧接4秒任务。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "7s",
        "4s",
        "1s",
        "after 5s"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，1秒任务的依赖写的是\"after 5s\"，但前面没有5秒的任务，这是指绝对时间点第5秒开始吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "1s",
        "after 5s"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，就是第5秒那个时间点。ID=2部分简单些：6秒从0开始，然后5秒的任务接在后面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section ID=2",
